00:07:41,900 --> 00:07:46,020
(Xishi Noodles)

89
00:07:46,080 --> 00:07:47,680
These people came for noodles so early!

90
00:07:48,120 --> 00:07:49,160
The noodles here
get very good reviews online!

91
00:07:49,200 --> 00:07:49,920
Sir,

92
00:07:50,840 --> 00:07:52,440
