137
00:09:00,120 --> 00:09:00,600
Mom.

138
00:09:00,640 --> 00:09:01,120
Yes?

139
00:09:01,160 --> 00:09:02,920
We still need to cook two bowls
of tomato and egg noodles for table 3.

140
00:09:03,160 --> 00:09:03,640
Oh, no!

141
