Tell me about it!
We've got so many customers today,

231
00:12:09,560 --> 00:12:10,840
but I don't feel tired at all!

232
00:12:11,240 --> 00:12:11,680
That's right.

233
00:12:12,040 --> 00:12:13,160
And there are barely

234
00:12:13,480 --> 00:12:14,280
