261
00:12:50,760 --> 00:12:51,480
that if we

262
00:12:51,520 --> 00:12:53,440
make some changes to the menu,

263
00:12:53,680 --> 00:12:54,600
we can double our turnover!

264
00:12:55,120 --> 00:12:55,640
Turnover?

265
00:12:56,720 --> 00:12:58,000
